snippet.textDisplay: Enough is enough!!wow!! I had a beautiful day. talk to people gave them love dancing for Jesus Christ. Doing the running Man to the throne room of Grace Hallelujah. Jesus Christ moving power against the spirit of the world against the spirit of fear against the spirit of ignorance. Jesus Christ is on the throne Holy Spirit speak of hearts minds and souls out there rise up From ashes to beauty. Jesus walked on water. Jesus rebuked the storm. JESUS said he get you through.
